[SPEAKER_24]: Yes.

194
00:16:14,407 --> 00:16:25,110
[SPEAKER_24]: And I will say, I can't imagine that somebody with a handicapped placard would prefer to park in front of your house when they were going to Playstead Road, or to Playstead Park, but they could.

