359
00:30:52,160 --> 00:31:06,814
[SPEAKER_22]: Why that's important is because sometimes if you have two lanes side by side approaching a crosswalk or even approaching the circle itself, the nearest lane will block the view of this outside lane here.

360
00:31:07,914 --> 00:31:09,415
[SPEAKER_22]: And that can be dangerous for pedestrians.

361
