362
00:31:12,436 --> 00:31:24,479
[SPEAKER_22]: So we made it kind of put these shoulders in with some flex posts to make sure that there's just one lane coming and going into the circle for all of the different streets intersecting.

363
00:31:24,499 --> 00:31:29,101
