1321
02:11:27,036 --> 02:11:32,818
[SPEAKER_04]: I'd rather have, if you're going to limit the parking, well, you know, I'll be upset about that, but the posts I absolutely object to.

1322
02:11:33,291 --> 02:11:36,234
