1340
02:12:52,412 --> 02:12:55,233
[SPEAKER_04]: She pulls in front to unload the babies and put them in the car.

1341
02:12:55,513 --> 02:12:59,855
[SPEAKER_04]: So remember, people who live here have families, have kids, more than one car.

1342
