[SPEAKER_10]: We're just speaking on the parking spots that would be lost for this bike lane.

1473
02:26:05,647 --> 02:26:07,527
[SPEAKER_10]: So obviously if the commissioners

1474
02:26:09,597 --> 02:26:19,941
[SPEAKER_10]: would like to speak further on this, table this motion or approve for certain portions of this.

1475
02:26:20,221 --> 02:26:32,466
[SPEAKER_10]: It seems like there are a lot of questions that have been raised by both commission and residents along with Amy and Todd have done a ton of work for this.

1476
